{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"417a1e257a","title":"读《明耻篇》后题词","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"52ae4c72c8","index":0,"year":1915,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"417a1e257a"}],"tags":[{"id":"4172b5fa3c","name":"九·一三事件","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1913-1943卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"1968年武汉","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e9a7261f35","type":"paragraph","text":"第一师范讲堂条","index":0,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"417a1e257a"},{"id":"f67f9b3d35","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九一三年十一月一日）","index":1,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"417a1e257a"},{"id":"e152ecb2bd","type":"paragraph","text":"修身。人情多耽安供而劳苦，情为万恶之渊。人而情，农则废其田时，工则废其规矩，商翼即废其所影，士则废其所学，业即废奖，无以为生，而杀身亡家乃随之奖。因而情，始则不进，即银行，则囊，整则灭亡，可畏载！故日情万恶之渊也。","index":2,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"417a1e257a"},{"id":"afe404b705","type":"paragraph","text":"奋斗。夫以五千之卒，敌十万之军。策黑乏之兵，当新属之马。如此欲图存而不亡，开奋斗不可。","index":3,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"417a1e257a"},{"id":"f9537f0596","type":"paragraph","text":"朝氟。少年须有朝气，否则气中之。幕气之来，乘疏解之陵也。故日意情者生之货嘉。","index":4,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"417a1e257a"},{"id":"fdd769862d","type":"paragraph","text":"清《明取篇》后题","index":5,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"417a1e257a"},{"id":"a111a5122b","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九一五年）","index":6,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"417a1e257a"},{"id":"14e21a7e7c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席在第一师范求学期间，了当时很多进步书刊。当他看了《明耶篇》以后，义懂旗胸，亲自笔在书上写道","index":7,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"417a1e257a"},{"id":"d090759ca6","type":"paragraph","text":"“五月七日，国民奇轮何以报仇，","index":8,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"417a1e257a"},{"id":"a5afa55d83","type":"paragraph","text":"在我学子！这十六个字充分表现了主席青少年时就立下了以天下为已任的革命的雄心壮志。","index":9,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"417a1e257a"},{"id":"baad685825","type":"paragraph","text":"《新青年》第七卷第一号","index":10,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"417a1e257a"},{"id":"41e791a898","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九一七年）","index":11,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"417a1e257a"},{"id":"20449cceed","type":"paragraph","text":"长沙受了“五四”运动的鼓动，一般人向新潮方面走的，实在不少，又因近年来层受重阀派的摧残，弄得长沙这锦锈的地方，常常没有一点生气，于是一般稍有知的人一各校教职员及学生—莫不深深痛恨。更觉得这《社会改造》、《思想革新》、《妇女解放》《民族自决》种种间题万不容爱。","index":12,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"417a1e257a"},{"id":"f6d76e7fcf","type":"paragraph","text":"1","index":13,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"417a1e257a"}],"page":{"id":"36c8858e02","publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"417a1e257a","start":10,"end":10}}}},"__N_SSG":true}